	pf_fastagi_args
	$Revision$
	$Date$
	FastAgi interface change (backport from Asterisk 1.6 for 1.4)

	XIVO needs this Asterisk 1.6 style fastagi interface, so we backported
	it for Asterisk 1.4.

	It was first done for Asterisk 1.2 by Richard Braun, I just refreshed
	it for Asterisk 1.4.

